This is how to solve of s:
   Remember that n is s's length
   Remember that i is 0
   Remember that result is []
   Do this n times:
      Remember that c is item i in s
      When c is at least 48, then:
         When c is at most 57, then:
            Add result to sum of 105 and (diff of 57 and c)
         But, if not:
            When c is at least 97, then:
               When c is at most 122, then:
                  Add result to diff of c and 32
               But, if not:
